Text.val: 23.04.2014 SH SCR18851 Test3: Added test on existing row in DBHS if NFIN_MARKCODE = 90 to skip GB101 (MC change)
We always delete NFIN and TINV if a match is found, only in case of change of mc
Change from no mc to mc in client file
mark code may have been changed by Heller so TINV may not be up to date
if this is of no interest we can use TINV_mc/NFIN_mc as Old/New

SQL_STMT_U.val: select NFIN_LINENO, TINV_NO from :1/NFIN join :1/TINV on TINV_ADMNO = NFIN_ADMNO and TINV_CLNTNO = NFIN_CLNTNO and TINV_DEBC_DEBC = NFIN_DEBC_DEBC and TINV_INVOICENO = NFIN_INVNO where NFIN_NFIR_NO = :2 for fetch only

select TINV_NO from :1/TINV where TINV_ADMNO = :2 and TINV_CLNTNO = :3 and exists (select * from :1/NFIN where NFIN_ADMNO = TINV_ADMNO and NFIN_CLNTNO = TINV_CLNTNO and NFIN_DEBC_DEBC = TINV_DEBC_DEBC and NFIN_INVNO = TINV_INVOICENO and NFIN_NFIR_NO = :4) for fetch only
